HtmlItemData.Html:
Service Quality Feedback Survey
 
 
Dear Customer,
In order to serve you better in the future, please take a few moments to tell us about the service that you have received.  Your business is appreciated and we want to make sure we meet your expectations.  Thank you.

ItemTexts_Select1Data.TextValue: With regards to your most recent customer service experience, how would you rate the quality of service you received?
In evaluating your experience, how would you rate the process of getting your issue resolved?
How would you rate the courteousness of the Customer Service Representative?
How would you rate the speed in which your call was handled by the Customer Service Representative?
How would you rate the knowledge of the Customer Service Representative that you spoke with?
How would you rate the time you waited to have your problem resolved?
Over the next 12 months, how likely are you to replace our product with another product or brand?

OptionTexts.TextValue: Had to explain problem more than once
Did not know how to handle problem
I was given the wrong information
I was not given a clear answer
Representative could not solve the problem

ItemTexts_MultiLineTextItemData.TextValue: Please describe if there was any particular aspect of the service experience that stood out:
Please describe if there was any particular aspect of the process that stood out:
Please provide any further information relating to your customer service experience below:

ItemTexts_MessageItemData.TextValue: Thank you for your time and honest feedback!

ItemTexts_SelectManyData.TextValue: Which of the following qualities came across as superior when dealing with the Customer Service Representative?
Which of the following qualities did you dislike when dealing with the Customer Service Representative?
What was your issue with the time taken?
What was your issue with the representative's knowledge?
